to the editor thomas l friedman offers us the letter he hopes president clinton will write to president hafez al assad of syria now that the israeli syrian talks have adjourned dear hafez column jan 11 let me add a paragraph dear hafez did you watch cnn this morning did you see that america online and time warner have merged this deal is many times larger than your annual gdp remember hafez the question is not whether israel is a part of the middle east but whether syria will become part of the 21st century avi ulman plainview ny jan 11 2000

